# API Testing Strategy

We use Djangoâ€™s APITestCase to validate endpoints.

## Tests
- CRUD: Create, Retrieve, Update, Delete Book
- Filtering: /api/books/?author__name=Chinua Achebe
- Searching: /api/books/?search=Fall
- Ordering: /api/books/?ordering=publication_year
- Permissions: Auth required for create/update/delete

## Running Tests
python manage.py test api